<br>
I'm about to start on a pretty serious 'comic book' story (to help my story telling skills and drawing skills in one shot), and it's something that alot of people don't really like.......But  for those who can sit through it, I'd really like some feedback:<br>
<br>
It's a pretty simple story, but there will be alot of underlying 'symbolism' in the final product. <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>WARNING</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Discretion is <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>strongly</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> advised. Graphic violence and drug use. You've been warned.<br>
<br>
VERY ROUGH OUTLINE<br>
<br>
-----------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
In present day,  a middle-class family moves out of thier old town, and moves to a new suburban area looking for a 'change of life'. The city is fairly large, and there's a population of about 10,000. This family (A father, mother, and 3 year old baby girl) move in, and at first, everything is fine. People seem nice, and everything seems peaceful. Until Halloween.<br>
<br>
A <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>very</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> elaborate gang (we'll just call them SHINRA...FF7, anyone? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) realize that this family is becoming a little too successful, and getting raises, while gang members who work at the same place are getting laid off. The gang kidnaps his wife and little girl, forcing him to 're-evaluate his options'. The father refuses to give up his job, so they inject his wife with an intense mix of Crank, Speed, and Heroine (sp?). She becomes the 'gang whore' in a sense, and she leaves her husband. SHINRA members go by him any chance they get, just to show him what his wife will do with other gang members.<br>
<br>
SHINRA kidnaps the father, and keeps him in a wharehouse. They force him to watch his wife cheating on him <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>multiple</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> times with random people. Then, they ask him about quitting his job, or leaving. Once again, the father refuses, causing SHINRA to kill his daughter in front of him. Afterwords, they beat him to a bloody pulp, and his wife spits in his face.<br>
<br>
......Then, the father snaps.<br>
<br>
He seeks revenge on this gang. He WILL take this gang down, by brutally killing each member one-by-one, the next more brutal then the previous. Stabbings, burnings, torture, etc are a few tricks up his sleeve......Payback's a bitch.<br>
----------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
That's a <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>very</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> basic outline, as this comic will easily be around 70-100 pages in length.<br>
<br>
I'm going for a 'justified violence/I can see where the antihero is coming from' feel (The Crow, Desperado, etc).<br>
<br>
Well, any feedback is appreciated. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :hat --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/pimp.gif ALT=":hat"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><center><img src="http://www.angelfire.com/indie/kami_v2/images/KamiProjectBanner.txt"><br><br></center><center><font color=black><b><small>Song Of The Moment: I Ran (So Far Away) - <i>Flock Of Seagulls</i></small></b></font></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=agentcryrid>Agent Cryrid</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(4/11/03 2:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Need some comments on story idea.....</span><hr size=1> Reminds me of Max Payne/Dead to Rights.<br>
