<br>
I realize this story revolves around the main male protagonist but as a woman reading the rough idea several things jumped out at me immediately.<br>
<br>
The setup for the woman's fall from grace needs to be handled very carefully. Not unlike a pregnant woman getting raped, or a &quot;good girl&quot; having lewd sex. It's not impossible but it needs to be done with incredible delicacy.<br>
<br>
You still need the readers to connect with the wife because otherwise it cheapens what the main character has lost. <br>
<br>
If this is intended as a graphic novel, or script, you might want to show snapshots of time passing and a Patty Hurst type of abuse and drug brainwashing. You might want to firmly establish, with action, that she can't end her own life without causing the termination of her daughter's.<br>
<br>
Go get'em... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thesilenthero>the silent hero</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pre-Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(5/31/03 2:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Need some comments on story idea.....</span><hr size=1> good, very good even if you need help with a torture scene<br>
